<p><strong>Saving Throws</strong> Dex +2, Con +4, Wis +2, Cha +4</p>

<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +4, Stealth +2</p>

<p><strong>Damage Immunities</strong> lightning</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> blindsight 10 ft., darkvision 60 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Draconic</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 3 (700 XP)</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 8 (1d10 + 3) piercing damage plus 3 (1d6) lightning damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Lightning Breath (Recharge 5-6).</em></strong> The dragon exhales lightning in a 30-foot line that is 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 22 (4d10) lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>

